&gt;&gt; Alda Migoni: Oh, thank you.

00:41:00.120 --> 00:41:05.300
Before closing there are still
a little time for questions.

00:41:05.300 --> 00:41:09.280
But we -- I do feel kind
of separated from Congress

00:41:09.280 --> 00:41:12.690
and I suppose you are our boss.

00:41:12.690 --> 00:41:13.990
There are a lot of times
when [inaudible response]

00:41:13.990 --> 00:41:15.290
and I just really appreciate
that you took the time to speak

00:41:15.290 --> 00:41:16.590
to us and to [inaudible] the
issues and to speak [inaudible].

00:41:16.590 --> 00:41:19.010
So that's great.

00:41:19.010 --> 00:41:20.750
We are a tunnel away.

00:41:20.750 --> 00:41:22.050
[Laughter].

